<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hatteras Nexus | Shred the Digital Ocean</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;700;900&display=swap');
        body { font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; scroll-behavior: smooth; background-color: #020617; overflow-x: hidden; }
        
        /* Animation 2: Neon Sunset Ripples & Magical Glows */
        .neon-sunset { 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff007f 0%, #ff8c00 50%, #00d2ff 100%);
            background-size: 400% 400%;
            animation: ripple 15s ease infinite;
        }
        @keyframes ripple {
            0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
            100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
        }
        .glass { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); backdrop-filter: blur(15px); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); }
        .surf-card:hover { transform: translateY(-10px) rotate(1deg); transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275); border-color: #ff007f; box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(255, 0, 127, 0.3); }
        .text-glow { text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.8); }
        .orb-glow { box-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.5), inset 0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 127, 0.5); }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="text-slate-100">

    <!-- NAV BAR -->
    <nav class="fixed w-full z-50 glass py-4 px-8 flex justify-between items-center border-b border-white/10">
        <div class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tighter uppercase italic text-glow">Hatteras<span class="text-cyan-400">Nexus</span></div>
        <div class="hidden lg:flex space-x-8 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">
            <a href="#pass" class="hover:text-pink-500 transition">Hatteras Pass</a>
            <a href="#sanctuary" class="hover:text-cyan-400 transition">Salvo Sanctuary</a>
            <a href="#quiver" class="hover:text-orange-500 transition">The Quiver</a>
            <a href="#fins" class="hover:text-teal-400 transition">Industry Fins</a>
        </div>
        <button class="bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-orange-500 text-white px-8 py-2 rounded-full font-black uppercase text-sm hover:scale-105 transition shadow-lg">Drop In</button>
    </nav>

    <!-- HERO: THE ATLANTIC SWELL -->
    <header class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center text-center px-4 neon-sunset">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-950/40"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl">
            <span class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-white/10 rounded-full text-white text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-8 border border-white/20">GPTSpeed Infrastructure</span>
            <h1 class="text-7xl md:text-9xl font-black mb-8 leading-none tracking-tighter uppercase">Don't Just Watch the Swell. <br><span class="text-cyan-300 italic font-light text-glow">Own the Ocean.</span></h1>
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-12 text-white max-w-3xl mx-auto font-medium">Experience the $9.4 Billion Digital Delta. From automated workflows to sovereign cloud mastery in the heart of the Outer Banks [1, 2].</p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-6">
                <a href="#pass" class="bg-white text-slate-900 px-12 py-5 rounded-full font-black text-xl hover:scale-110 transition shadow-2xl">GET THE $17 PASS</a>
                <a href="#quiver" class="glass px-12 py-5 rounded-full font-black text-xl hover:bg-white/10 transition border border-white/30 uppercase italic">View the Quiver</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- THE HATTERAS PASS: $17 MEMBERSHIP -->
    <section id="pass" class="py-32 px-8 bg-slate-950 relative">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-20 items-center">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2">
                <h2 class="text-6xl font-black mb-8 leading-tight tracking-tighter uppercase">The <span class="text-pink-500">Hatteras Pass</span></h2>
                <div class="text-5xl font-black mb-6 text-white text-glow">$17<span class="text-sm font-normal text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest ml-2 italic">/ month recurring</span></div>
                <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-10 leading-relaxed">Shred the admin and automate your life. Why pay $2,220/mo for legacy bloat when you can have the **Digital Pipeline** for the price of a fish taco? [3, 4]</p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 group">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-cyan-500/20 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-cyan-500 transition"><i class="fa-solid fa-microphone-lines text-cyan-400 group-hover:text-slate-900"></i></div>
                        <div><h4 class="font-bold text-white">Sea Mist Orb</h4><p class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase">Voice AI CRM [5]</p></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 group">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-orange-500/20 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-orange-500 transition"><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line text-orange-400 group-hover:text-slate-900"></i></div>
                        <div><h4 class="font-bold text-white">Surf Sensei</h4><p class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase">AI Sales Coach [6]</p></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 glass p-12 rounded-[3rem] orb-glow relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-40 h-40 bg-pink-500 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-20"></div>
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-black mb-8 uppercase italic tracking-tighter">Member Benefits</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-6">
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-300 font-bold"><i class="fa-solid fa-bolt text-yellow-400"></i> 80% Faster Dashboard Loads [5]</li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-300 font-bold"><i class="fa-solid fa-phone text-teal-400"></i> BYOK Calling ($0.013/min) [7]</li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-300 font-bold"><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-check text-pink-400"></i> 37+ Visual Workflow Actions [8]</li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-300 font-bold"><i class="fa-solid fa-users text-cyan-400"></i> Team Collaboration Revolution [9]</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SALVO SANCTUARY: JOHNNY BULL HOOPER -->
    <section id="sanctuary" class="py-32 px-8 bg-slate-900 border-y border-white/5 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-2 neon-sunset opacity-50"></div>
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
            <span class="text-pink-500 font-black tracking-[0.5em] uppercase text-xs mb-6 block">Memorial: Salvo is Special</span>
            <h2 class="text-7xl md:text-8xl font-black text-white italic uppercase tracking-tighter mb-8 text-glow">Johnny Bull Hooper</h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-400 mb-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto">A legendary ride in the Salvo Sanctuary. Drop-in your respects and keep the history of the Diamond Shoals alive [History].</p>
            
            <div class="glass p-10 rounded-[3rem] text-left border-t-4 border-cyan-400">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 uppercase"><i class="fa-solid fa-water text-cyan-400"></i> The Respects Barrel</h3>
                <div class="space-y-6 mb-12" id="respects-feed">
                    <div class="border-l-2 border-pink-500 pl-6 py-2">
                        <p class="text-slate-300 italic text-lg leading-relaxed">"Johnny Bull always knew the swell better than anyone. Salvo won't be the same without his spirit in the lineup."</p>
                        <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 mt-2 block">— Cape Point Crew</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button class="w-full bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-2xl text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm transition">
                    + Add Your Respects to the Sanctuary
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- THE QUIVER: CORE TIERS -->
    <section id="quiver" class="py-32 px-8 bg-slate-950">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center mb-24">
            <h2 class="text-6xl font-black mb-4 tracking-tighter uppercase italic">The Big Wave Quiver</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-500 uppercase font-bold tracking-[0.3em]">Hatteras Automation Tiers [1, 10]</p>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
            <!-- Tier 3: Navigator -->
            <div class="glass p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] surf-card border-t-8 border-cyan-400">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 uppercase">Soundside Cruiser</h3>
                <div class="text-3xl font-black mb-8">$499<span class="text-sm font-normal text-slate-500 uppercase">/mo</span></div>
                <ul class="text-sm space-y-4 text-slate-400 font-bold">
                    <li>🏄 50,000 AI Workflow Drops</li>
                    <li>🏄 5 Team Seats</li>
                    <li>🏄 Full API Access</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <!-- Tier 5: Lighthouse -->
            <div class="glass p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] surf-card border-t-8 border-pink-500 bg-pink-500/5">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 uppercase">Cape Point Keeper</h3>
                <div class="text-3xl font-black mb-8">$1,299<span class="text-sm font-normal text-slate-500 uppercase">/mo</span></div>
                <ul class="text-sm space-y-4 text-slate-300 font-bold">
                    <li>🚀 250,000 AI Workflow Drops</li>
                    <li>🚀 20 Team Seats</li>
                    <li>🚀 <b>Priority Line Processing</b></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <!-- Tier 6: Scale -->
            <div class="glass p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] surf-card border-t-8 border-orange-500">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 uppercase">Diamond Shoals Pro</h3>
                <div class="text-3xl font-black mb-8">$3,499<span class="text-sm font-normal text-slate-500 uppercase">/mo</span></div>
                <ul class="text-sm space-y-4 text-slate-400 font-bold">
                    <li>🏢 1,000,000 AI Workflow Drops</li>
                    <li>🏢 Unlimited Seats</li>
                    <li>🏢 Dedicated Infrastructure</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <!-- Tier 7: Elite -->
            <div class="glass p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] surf-card border-t-8 border-purple-500">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 uppercase text-purple-400 text-glow">Graveyard Sovereign</h3>
                <div class="text-3xl font-black mb-8">$7,999<span class="text-sm font-normal text-slate-500 uppercase">/mo</span></div>
                <ul class="text-sm space-y-4 text-slate-400 font-bold">
                    <li>👑 Unlimited AI Drops</li>
                    <li>👑 On-Premise Reef</li>
                    <li>👑 Dedicated Surf Sensei</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- INDUSTRY FINS: SPECIALIZED MODULES -->
    <section id="fins" class="py-32 px-8 bg-slate-900 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-5xl font-black mb-16 uppercase italic tracking-tighter text-center">Industry-Specific <span class="text-cyan-400">Fins</span></h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-4">
                <div class="glass p-6 rounded-2xl text-center hover:bg-cyan-500 hover:text-slate-900 transition font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">Real Estate [11]</div>
                <div class="glass p-6 rounded-2xl text-center hover:bg-pink-500 hover:text-slate-900 transition font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">E-Commerce [12]</div>
                <div class="glass p-6 rounded-2xl text-center hover:bg-orange-500 hover:text-slate-900 transition font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">Non-Profit [13]</div>
                <div class="glass p-6 rounded-2xl text-center hover:bg-teal-500 hover:text-slate-900 transition font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">MedTech [11]</div>
                <div class="glass p-6 rounded-2xl text-center hover:bg-purple-500 hover:text-slate-900 transition font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">Legal [14]</div>
                <div class="glass p-6 rounded-2xl text-center hover:bg-yellow-500 hover:text-slate-900 transition font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">Restaurants [15]</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FOOTER CTA -->
    <footer class="py-40 px-8 text-center bg-slate-950 relative">
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-1 neon-sunset"></div>
        <h2 class="text-7xl font-black mb-8 uppercase italic tracking-tighter text-glow">Ready to catch the swell?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-400 mb-16">14-Day Free Ride. No Credit Card. Under 1-Hour Setup [3].</p>
        <button class="bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-orange-500 text-white px-20 py-8 rounded-full font-black text-3xl uppercase tracking-tighter hover:scale-110 transition shadow-[0_0_60px_rgba(255,0,127,0.5)] mb-20">Activate AI Now</button>
        <div class="pt-20 border-t border-white/5 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.5em] text-slate-700">
            © 2026 Hatteras Nexus Technologies | Digital Delta Sovereign Infrastructure [2].
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
